title: Chanel Sweater Dress
description:
Deep navy Chanel sweater dress with open chain crochet top and Chanel logo knitted into the hip area.

Super cute and I have worn it some, but feel it's a little too big on me as I am more of a 36/38.  

Super stretchy knit, so it could probably be fine for even somewhat larger than a usual 40.  Flattering a-line shape that works well for bigger hips.  Sometimes sweater dresses are a no-go for hippier people like me, but this one works.

No real issues, just some fuzz.  I keep forgetting to buy one of those things that take the fuzz off.  When I remember, I will pick one up and go over the dress with it.

Yes, it is authentic and has all the labels to prove that it is pictured, and anything over 500 automatically goes straight to PM headquarters to be authenticated before shipping to you.  There is an ungodly amount of Chanel on here that is not authentic, but this one is the real deal.

Good weight for fall, winter, or spring.  I wore it as a work dress primarily with leggings and tall brown boots.  Also looks great with a belt at the waist in between the crochet to knit transition.

Wool and cashmere blend.

Pit to pit is 17 inches unstretched and waist is about the same.  Back of neck to bottom hem is about 35 inches.

Thanks for looking!  Check out my closet for lots of other higher end clothing, shoes, and bags.

Top rated seller, superfast shipper, and PM ambassador.
